1. *Nek* razumno postupiš (May you act wisely).
2. Poželiću mu da *nek* bude srećan (I will wish him to be happy).
3. *Nek* pronađe svoju sreću (May he find his happiness).
4. *Nek* bude večeras lepo (May it be nice tonight).
5. *Nek* se držiš svojih planova (May you stick to your plans).
6. *Nek* bude sve kako treba (May everything be as it should).